Text.string: Heyyy! Numbah. One. Hammy. Lock. Rescuer. BOOM!
Whaaaat?! Aurelia's EVIL? Whaaaaat?
Vaulty Vault! Hammylock and Winnybutt double-rescuer! Boom!
Is every ladygirl I know a frackin' Siren?! Okay, I'mma need everyone to get buck naked RIGHT NOW and I'm CHECKIN' FOR TATS!
Apocalypse party! We blowin' up this whole muthahumpa!
How's hangin' with Typhoid DeLorean?
THIS WHOLE PLANET'S ABOUT TO POP THE FRICK OFF!
Girl, we plowed that Tyreeny-weenie beyotch into the freakin' GROUND!
What up?
Holla!
I never loved nothin' like I love me some bombs and if I ever do, I'mma blow it the hell up. That's just some facts right there.

Kinda startin' to contemplate my own mortality, y'know? I mean, I'm pushin' twenty and that's like a burdillion in Pandora years. Might be time to hang up the old boomy-dooms and retire to that farm for abandoned skags I've been talkin' 'bout.
Oh, you lookin' for boom? 'Cause I gots the boom.
Baby, you knooooow better than to show up here without cupcakes. All right, you okay this time. But watch yo ass.
Shorty, you a full stack of wafflecakes. You gotta pour some syrup on dat ass.
Plph, plp-psh, pltp-pltp-plptsh—agh, I'm bad at beatboxing.
S'up, haters? Just kidding, I know you love you some T-swag.
I love you, but I'm gonna need you to back the hell off. Okay? I NEED MAH SPACE!
Oh, me? I'm just musin' 'bout the meaning of life, the universe, and, uh, big ol' juicy butts. The uzhe.

You ever think about how many people we've killed? How many lives we've snuffed out, removing all hope for redemption, condemning our victims to eternal judgment because of our petty whims and desire for loot and glory?||—Me neither, BIIIITCH!
You saved my man Hammylock, and that means we tight for life. LIFE, SON!
That Jakobs house looks stuffy as heck, but, y'know, I hear there's a secret crumpet closet and you KNOW I'm gonna find it!
Man, dads are overrated. Teach you how to ride bikes and shiz?||—Actually, that sounds kinda nice. Damn.
Vault guy's dead, huh? Well, y'know, it's like they say, uh...||—What were we talkin' about?
Man. Big-Lilly-Style made the biggest boom of all time.||—She'll be back. She's always back.
[humming] Doin' a hum. Heyyyy.
Bittie gonna come at me, like “why'd you blow up my house?” You knoooow what you did.
Hooh! Bomb inside another bomb. Donezo! Oh, no no—bomb that shoots other bombs. Oooh! No, no! Bombs that KISS and make a third bomb. Yeah... yeah... mmmhmhmhm.
Maybe I shouldn't have competed in the Demolitions Universal Cup and the Sex Olympics of Eroticon 6 in the same month. Got my routines switched up. But let's just say... I got kicked out of both.
That Clay fella looks like a whole punch bowl fulla trouble, and here I am holdin' a ladle.||—Shut up! Goggles is hot. You don't know me.
You smell like teddy bear, what gives? And do I detect a whiff of horny monkey?
Yo. I heard you went undercover in the deeeep swamp. You get me anything?
Hah! More like BORE-elia. Got her!||—She IS dead, though.
I am definitely stealin' that big-ass Carnivora skull for the hideouts!
Heard you rolled up in some dark spooky mine. Spooky dooky. A scooby-dooby-doot-doot dooky.
What, so another adorable unstable teen with a dark past shows up and she gets Siren powers IMMEDIATELY?! This is bullcrap.
Yo, bring me somethin' back from that alien planet. Like some... like some rocks or somethin'. Like—like, weird ones, that make you feel weird. Bring me some of those.
Vaulty Vault! Got a missióné, when you feels up to it.
Hey. Hey. Heyheyheyhey. Gotta mission for you. Hey.
I got a new mission, IF YOU CAN FIND ME! Nah, I'm at the same ol' place.
Vaulty Vault!
S'uuuuup.
What that thang do? Seriously, what that thang do?
Hey girl heyyy!
Hellooooo.
Yo, I'm plannin' a thing. You in?
Oh, you want in on this. Trust me.
If do zis for me... zen ze incident of ze Scarlet Diamond will be forgotten.
It's gonna be fuuuuun!
Please? Please! PLEASE! Please.
You still doin' that buttcrap?
How's that thingy thing goin'?
Did you do it?||—I know you didn't do it.
Oh, Margarest, you must tell me more about THAT MISSION YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO BE DOIN'!
So. You gonna... take care of that little thing we talked about, or...?
Catch you on the flippity-dip.
There you go, to save the day.
Bye!
Oodles of toodles.
B-Team, biiiitch!
Cheese it, it's the fuzz!
I can't be held responsible for what happens when you leave me alone, okay? IT'S ON YOUR HEAD!
Oh, I buried some mines over—nah, you'll figure it out.
You DARE? In MY HOUSE?!
Bon voyage!
